Class SemAnnot

java.lang.Object
  ex.reader.Annot
      ex.reader.SemAnnot
All Implemented Interfaces:
Annotable
public class SemAnnot
extends Annot
implements Annotable

SemAnnot represents a semantic annotation. Depending on type, its data can e.g. point to a definition of a model attribute or class, or to a parse chunk produced by 3rd party syntactic parser.
